title: Font suggestion similar to Cubesity Rounded
content:
Can somebody suggest fonts which are similar to Cubesity Rounded ( [http://www.dafont.com/cubesity-rounded.font](http://web.archive.org/web/20131017160012/http:/www.dafont.com/cubesity-rounded.font "http://www.dafont.com/cubesity-rounded.font")).  
Preferrably something which is a little bit easier to read, but still retains the blocky rounded style.
